Feng Yang.

100
00:08:49,830 --> 00:08:50,350
Feng Yang.

101
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:57,950
In fact,

102
00:08:58,390 --> 00:08:59,270
there is one thing

103
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,350
that you don't know.

104
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,000
This sword buckle doesn't represent

105
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:19,680
