107
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:26,470
My heart.

108
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:31,030
Prince Consort, do you know
what you are talking about?

109
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:31,680
Feng Yang.

110
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,470
I fell in love with you

111
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,510
