112
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:40,440
When I was forced to have a peace-making marriage,

113
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,510
the only thought that supported me

114
00:09:42,950 --> 00:09:44,350
was being able to meet you again.

115
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:47,510
I can overcome

116
00:09:48,030 --> 00:09:49,200
