117
00:09:51,390 --> 00:09:52,590
The only thing that supports me

118
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,470
is seeing you again.

119
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,950
You are Main Prince Consort of Second Princess.

120
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,080
