122
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,560
The marriage wasn't consummated.

123
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:06,910
Princess.

124
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,030
What do you mean?

125
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:10,830
On the wedding night,

126
00:10:10,950 --> 00:10:12,270
everything Yun Xiu did

127
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:13,680
was for Officer Xiao to see.

128
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:15,000
Instead of consummating the marriage,

129
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:17,120
he made a deal with me.

130
00:10:17,350 --> 00:10:18,560
If I help him pursue you,

131
00:10:18,830 --> 00:10:20,320
he would help me annoy Mo Lian Cheng.

132
00:10:22,510 --> 00:10:23,800
You were acting.

133
00:10:23,830 --> 00:10:25,350
Acting is an expedient measure.

134
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,240
But my feelings are genuine.

135
00:10:28,350 --> 00:10:30,030
If your feelings are genuine,

136
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:32,470
then you wouldn't have
hidden the truth from everyone,

137
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:35,000
and manipulated others like your puppets.

138
00:10:35,510 --> 00:10:35,950
Feng Yang.

139
00:10:35,950 --> 00:10:36,640
Shut up.

140
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,440
I don't want to see you anymore.

141
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,560
Neither do I want to hear you calling my name.

142
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:46,510
I'll move out of Princess's Residence immediately.

143
00:10:47,910 --> 00:10:48,800
Good luck to you.

144
00:10:49,510 --> 00:10:50,240
Feng Yang.

145
00:11:13,830 --> 00:11:14,880
Maybe she is just

146
