their heart closed is not Yun Xiu,

163
00:11:40,350 --> 00:11:41,320
it's Mo Feng Yang.

164
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:43,510
If you can really put yourself in each other's shoes,

165
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:44,710
you will realize

166
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:45,830
that in a relationship,

167
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:48,710
if tactics that you look down on are missing,

168
00:11:49,390 --> 00:11:51,150
it will be boring.

169
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:54,240
Are you talking about Yun Xiu or me?

170
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,800
Even though we have been married for a long time,

171
00:11:58,150 --> 00:12:00,440
