175
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:10,830
This is different.

176
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:13,270
Asking you to be a little more romantic

177
00:12:13,390 --> 00:12:14,880
can turn you into a different person?

178
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:17,270
Are those superficial things
that important to you?

179
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,560
Are things that you don't understand

180
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:19,800
superficial?

181
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:24,320
You don't even want to answer me now?

182
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,150
In this world,

183
00:12:30,470 --> 00:12:31,880
no relationships are the same.

184
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,200
No relationships

185
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,470
are comparable.

186
00:12:34,830 --> 00:12:36,150
Is asking you to be a little more romantic

187
00:12:36,350 --> 00:12:37,710
and to make changes

188
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,350
this difficult?

189
00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:40,680
You always think

190
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:41,680
about what makes you happy.

191
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:43,710
