202
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:27,140
♪I really want to write you a letter,
telling you I am still here♪

203
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:29,890
♪Waiting to hear from you♪

204
00:14:32,430 --> 00:14:36,560
♪I really want to send you a message,
