212
00:14:58,710 --> 00:14:59,240
I...

213
00:14:59,710 --> 00:15:01,510
I know you haven't eaten for the whole day.

214
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:02,880
I came to ask you to go eat.

215
00:15:05,680 --> 00:15:06,950
How did the character "yun"

216
00:15:06,950 --> 00:15:08,320
