217
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:11,950
Go away.

218
00:15:31,910 --> 00:15:32,470
Jing Xuan.

219
00:15:32,710 --> 00:15:33,440
Did she

220
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:36,350
really not eat for the whole day?

221
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:37,640
And when she was practicing calligraphy,

222
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,510
