228
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:56,760
"Ocean makes all other waters unworthy of the name,

229
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,760
after Wushan mountain, all other clouds
are mere puffballs above."

230
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:02,510
Don't worry.

231
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:03,830
I promise

232
00:16:03,950 --> 00:16:05,390
that after telling her one sentence,

233
00:16:05,470 --> 00:16:07,760
she'll recover immediately.

234
00:16:07,800 --> 00:16:08,510
What sentence?

235
00:16:11,080 --> 00:16:14,590
See you at five o'clock by Wangyou Lake.

236
00:16:14,760 --> 00:16:15,510
That's it?

237
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:16,950
That's it.

238
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:18,120
You're in charge of telling her.

239
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:19,270
I'm in charge

240
00:16:19,270 --> 00:16:20,240
of making a miracle happen.

241
00:16:20,390 --> 00:16:20,910
This...

242
00:16:21,680 --> 00:16:22,270
Be quick.

243
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:24,000
Be quick, be quick.

244
00:16:35,680 --> 00:16:36,390
Yun Xiu.

245
00:16:37,390 --> 00:16:38,230
Stop practicing.

246
00:16:39,510 --> 00:16:40,680
Save your energy for meeting Mo Feng Yang

247
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:43,110
at five o'clock.

248
00:16:43,510 --> 00:16:44,560
Did she finally ask me out?

249
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,840
Not yet.

250
00:16:47,230 --> 00:16:49,080
But if you follow my instructions,

251
00:16:49,560 --> 00:16:50,320
five o'clock

252
00:16:50,560 --> 00:16:52,720
will be the moment that determines your fate.

253
00:16:58,750 --> 00:17:00,200
Someone should stay away,

254
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:02,480
or our tactics will

255
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:04,150
lower his level.

256
00:17:05,840 --> 00:17:06,870
You're here.

257
00:17:25,390 --> 00:17:26,080
It looks like

258
00:17:26,630 --> 00:17:27,840
he used your tactics

259
00:17:28,080 --> 00:17:29,320
against you.

260
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:31,110
What do you mean?

261
00:17:31,630 --> 00:17:32,360
Playing hard to get.

262
00:17:32,750 --> 00:17:33,480
Intentionally giving you the cold shoulder.

263
00:17:38,390 --> 00:17:39,270
Well.

264
00:17:40,030 --> 00:17:40,750
Then

265
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,600
don't ever talk to me again.

266
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:56,270
After seeing the clouds of Wushan Mountain,

267
00:17:57,560 --> 00:17:58,680
how can I still

268
00:17:59,360 --> 00:18:00,990
look at other clouds?
[*This is a reference to the previous poem]

269
00:18:14,680 --> 00:18:15,390
Sister, Sister.

270
00:18:16,270 --> 00:18:17,150
My kite is coming down.

271
00:18:17,150 --> 00:18:18,150
Please help me.

272
00:18:18,230 --> 00:18:18,910
Okay.

273
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:25,990
Sister, you are great.

274
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:27,320
Is this higher?

275
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:51,200
It's time to reel it back.

276
00:18:53,440 --> 00:18:54,440
It's you?

277
00:19:01,030 --> 00:19:02,030
Don't move.

278
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:07,980
♪Another late autumn, another night,
the swallow has returned, when will you?♪

279
00:19:08,100 --> 00:19:11,810
♪Should the yellowing red letters
be taken down or not♪

280
